<H3> <TI>   10,000 Rally in Support of Jansa </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2803192594 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 1856 GMT 28 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2803192594 </F>
