  [Excerpt] Ljubljana, 28 Mar (TANJUG) -- Around 10,000 
supporters of compromised Slovene Defense Minister Janez Jansa 
continued their rally in support of Jansa in front of the 
parliament building in Ljubljana this evening. Surrounded by a 
police cordon, angry demonstrators are demanding the removal of 
