<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Crvenkovski-Daskalov Meeting"] </F>
  [Text] Macedonian [The Former Yugoslav Republic on 
Macedonia -- FYROM] Foreign Minister Stevo Crvenkovski, together 
with his associates, met with the Bulgarian counterpart 
Stanislav Daskalov, who paused in Skopje on his way to Albania. 
The talks focused on future development of Macedonian-Bulgarian 
relations and cooperation. Both ministers stressed the need to 
intensify and regulate mutual economic and traffic relations, in 
spite of present sanctions and blockades. 

