<F P=100> SLOVENIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Defense Minister Jansa Impeached; Kacin Appointed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU2903071094 Ljubljana Radio Slovenia Network in Slovene 
0500 GMT 29 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU2903071094 </F>
<F P=104>  Ljubljana Radio Slovenia Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Slovene </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Last night, after a nine-hour extraordinary session 
on the impeachment of the defense minister, the State Chamber 
deputies, with 49 votes in favor and 39 against, relieved Janez 
Jansa of the duty of defense minister. With 48 votes in favor 
and 39 votes against, Jelko Kacin became the new defense 
minister. 

</TEXT>

