  [Text] Warsaw, March 27 -- The centre-right groupings are 
concerned over "Russian Defence Minister, General Pavel 
Grachev's statement about creating military fortified region 
around Kaliningrad and with a lack of reaction of Waldemar 
Pawlak's government to it," reads communique forwarded to PAP 
