Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Sofia, March 30 (BTA) -- In the course of his formal 
visit to Albania completed yesterday, Bulgarian Foreign Minister 
Stanislav Daskalov and his Albanian partners expressed a wish to 
promote bilateral relations to build up trust in the Balkans. 
Foreign Ministry spokesman Radko Vlaykov today met the press to 
elaborate on the visit. 
  Asked if Bulgaria and Albania differed on the UN Security 
Council decision to send Turkish peacekeepers to former 
