UNPROFOR [UN Protection Forces]. 
  Vlaykov said during a joint press conference of the 
Bulgarian 
and Albanian foreign ministers in Tirana yesterday, Daskalov was 
asked about the Bulgarian position on Kosovo. He said Bulgaria 
opposed any interference by foreign forces in seeking a solution 
to this internal problem. 

