  [Text] Warsaw, March 29 -- Dariusz Rosati remains the 
coalition candidate to the post of deputy prime minister and 
finance minister. The coalition hopes to meet soon with 
President Lech Walesa to present its arguments in the matter, 
General Secretary of the Social-Democracy of the Republic of 
Poland (SDRP) Jerzy Szmajdzinski said following a meeting held 
