minister and finance minister. He added that the meeting with 
the president may be held next week. 
  A visit of a Polish parliamentary delegation to Moscow, 
starting on Wednesday, was another topic of the meeting. 
Kwasniewski said that after returning from Moscow he may meet 
with Rosati who is on his way to Poland. 

